However, a bus can also have an accident or brake sharply at the moment in which the steward carries coffee or newspapers.
It also plays a role whether the bus is also equipped with standing places according to the vehicle letter.
If this is not provided on the bus, the passengers must sit.
Student Agency’s long-distance coaches do not have standing places, as the director of the company, Radim Jan<0xC4><0x8D>ura, confirmed to Aktu<0xC3><0xA1>ln<0xC4><0x9B>.cz.
