The driver of the bus tried to dodge by a sharp maneuver, but collided with the right front part of the truck.
Jan<0xC4><0x8D>ura denies that the two seats had been sold for the stewards.
"These places cannot be reserved for long-distance connections, they are blocked."
Company wants to sue truck drivers.
With compensation for the young woman’s family, the agency will not wait for the court ruling, but will also expect financial compensation from the guilty party.
A law change?
Not in sight
A more precise regulation of the movement of stewards on board a bus could bring a legal regulation, which a thirty-person team of experts from the Ministry of Transport has been working on for over a year.
“However, this has not yet reached a concrete conclusion.
